title: Bobby’s Valentine’s Day + Travis Denning Plays Banjo In Studio + Bobby’s Mailbag: Wife Finds Husband’s Secret Girlfriend + Edwin McCain Performs “I’ll Be” In Studio
itunes:title: Bobby’s Valentine’s Day + Travis Denning Plays Banjo In Studio + Bobby’s Mailbag: Wife Finds Husband’s Secret Girlfriend + Edwin McCain Performs “I’ll Be” In Studio
description:
Bobby talks about his Valentine’s Day. Bobby invites Travis Denning into the studio to perform “What’s My Age Again” by Blink 182 and a couple other songs on his banjo! A listener writes in that she discovered her husband has a secret girlfriend while gaming. Edwin McCain stops by to talk about his song “I’ll Be” and performs it for us!
